    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市将因利率担忧重燃而下滑：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们再次担心美联储将在更长时间内维持高利率，助长了美国基准股指的抛售，并推高了债券收益率和美元，亚洲股市将于 5 月开盘走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维京邮轮 IPO 融资 15.4 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cruise-line-viking-holdings-ipo-is-said-to-fetch-1-54-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，维京控股有限公司 (Viking Holdings Ltd.) 的首次公开募股定价接近市场定价区间的上限，为这家豪华游轮运营商和两名投资者筹集 15.4 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/cruise-line-viking-holdings-ipo-is-said-to-fetch-1-54-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:28:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元的剧烈波动只是未来的一个尝试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-30/jpy-usd-japanese-yen-s-slide-and-dramatic-rebound-are-just-the-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[除非深层次的结构性问题得到解决，否则剧烈波动可能会变得更加频繁。其影响远远超出了日本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-30/jpy-usd-japanese-yen-s-slide-and-dramatic-rebound-are-just-the-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多耗资250亿美元的跨山铁路运输石油获得最终许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/trans-mountain-pipeline-gets-final-regulatory-clearance-to-ship-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[跨山管道的扩建获得了开始将原油从油砂运输到加拿大太平洋海岸所需的最终监管许可，结束了这个有争议的项目长达十年的等待。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/trans-mountain-pipeline-gets-final-regulatory-clearance-to-ship-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道明银行在美国洗钱调查中获得 4.5 亿美元赔偿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/td-takes-450-million-provision-in-us-money-laundering-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行 (Toronto-Dominion Bank) 已就美国对其反洗钱行为的调查初步拨备 4.5 亿美元，并表示预计还将面临更多处罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/td-takes-450-million-provision-in-us-money-laundering-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗表示，交易员预计标准普尔指数将出现自 2023 年以来的最大美联储日波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/traders-expect-biggest-fed-day-move-in-s-p-since-2023-citi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期权市场对标准普尔 500 指数因美联储周三的利率决定而可能出现的大幅波动的担忧程度，比近一年来的任何时候都要高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/traders-expect-biggest-fed-day-move-in-s-p-since-2023-citi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:36:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>看到企业客户之间在现金利率上的分歧：富国银行的麦克迈克尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/seeing-divide-between-corporate-clients-on-cash-rates-wells-fargo-s-mcmichael</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行企业和公共实体战略主管凡妮莎·麦克迈克尔(Vanessa McMichael)表示，一些客户正在利用美联储可能长期暂停的机会来维持现金利率，而其他客户则看到了机会。她与彭博社的 Romaine Bostick 和 Alix Steel 就“彭博市场：收盘”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/seeing-divide-between-corporate-clients-on-cash-rates-wells-fargo-s-mcmichael</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PG&E 与 KKR 就出售 Power Unit 少数股权进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pg-e-in-talks-with-kkr-to-sell-minority-stake-in-power-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PG&amp;E Corp. 正在洽谈将其发电业务的少数股权出售给投资公司 KKR &amp; Company。 Co.，交易监管机构已表示不打算支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pg-e-in-talks-with-kkr-to-sell-minority-stake-in-power-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦·巴菲特的 PacifiCorp 现在面临 300 亿美元的火灾索赔要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/buffett-s-pacificorp-now-faces-30-billion-fire-claim-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 旗下的 PacifiCorp 目前面临 2020 年俄勒冈州劳动节野火受害者索要 300 亿美元的索赔，这是对美国西部最大电网运营商的法律攻击升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/buffett-s-pacificorp-now-faces-30-billion-fire-claim-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:54:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
